Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Gallina Centro is located in Collierville, TN, approximately 17 miles southeast of downtown Memphis, TN.  Collierville is one of the more affluent suburbs in the Memphis area, with an average household income of  $161,000 annually. Collierville is a predominantly white-collar community with almost 85% of the workforce employed in white-collar jobs.  Additionally, Collierville is home to a highly educated population with 77% of its adults achieving a college or advanced degree.  This is more than double the national average.
